data.description: Motivated Seller! This property offers a large cul-de-sac lot and is a rare find in Bedford TX. The property has new flooring, paint and water heater. In the backyard is a huge storage building that can easily be wired for electricity to make it a great workshop or entertaining space.  Bedford has a lot to offer with numerous restaurants, bars, theaters, parks and shopping within 10 minutes from this location.  Go and Show this property.
